fields.body:
### Script created by Adam Willford for Rewst ###

### Set Execution Policy - Modified by Dhayes to comment Set-ExecutionPolicy because of Ninja errors 07-19-2023 ###

#Set-ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue

### Create object for results ###

$PS_Results = [System.Collections.Generic.List[object]]::new()

### Define some Variables as required ###

$userToCopyGuid = "{{ CTX.userToCopy }}"

### Identify the user from the GUID and return the UPN ###

try {
    $copyFromUserInformation = Get-ADUser $userToCopyGuid | Select-Object GivenName, Surname, UserPrincipalName, Enabled, SamAccountName, @{Label = 'SID'; Expression = { $_.SID.AccountDomainSid.Value } }, DistinguishedName, Name, ObjectGUID  
    $PS_Results.Add($copyFromUserInformation)
}
catch {
    $PS_Results.Add("Failure: User that we tried to identify -  ($userToCopyGuid) not found. Error if supplied was: $($_.Exception.Message)")
}

### Send all the data back to RewstyRewst ###

$postData = $PS_Results | ConvertTo-Json
Invoke-RestMethod -Method 'Post' -Uri $post_url -Body $postData -ContentType 'application/json; charset=utf-8'

publish.value:
{{-
    [
        result.id
        for result in RESULT.result.data["items"]
        if
            result.offerName|lower == CTX.offername_for_csp|lower
            and
            (result.commitmentEndDate | format_datetime) > (now() | convert_from_epoch | format_datetime)
            and
            result.status == "active"
    ][0] or none
-}}
